# Regenerable pipeline data — the runners fetch/build these from live sources on every run, and
# Render's filesystem is ephemeral, so they're NOT committed (keeps the repo lean). Frozen model
# inputs that ARE committed: *.pkl (models), *.xlsx (Madden), the small *_importance.csv.
**/*.parquet
*/data/*.json
*/data/h1tt_snapshots/
*/data/props_snapshots/
*/data/event_odds/
*/data/odds_history/
*/data/pbp_cache/
*/data/cfbd/
*/data/props_rows_*.csv
*/out/*.csv
